{"tid":404324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下體卡喺啞鈴片中間個窿 健身男要消防員解救","createTime":"2017-09-18T04:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T09:38:25.000Z","uid":22869,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4545470d48b6f941c08dfe03dc49fd7f4ab86ab5","tid":404324,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/18/123155_87c0f3e08c33d16f2fabb1b87517fefb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F18%2F123155_87c0f3e08c33d16f2fabb1b87517fefb.jpg&h=6596c97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">消防員用切割器材將啞鈴片切碎(互聯網)</span><br />\n<br />\n德國一名男子下體卡在一塊啞鈴片中央的洞，消防員花了三小時幫他解困。<br />\n<br />\n意外上周五在一間健身室發生。男子下體卡在2.5公斤的啞鈴片，要送院救治。<br />\n<br />\n消防員用切割器材將啞鈴片切碎，方能為男子的「小弟弟」解圍。他將可完全康復。<br />\n<br />\n沃爾姆斯（Worms）消防員事後在facebook展示切碎了的啞鈴片，提醒公眾不要效法該名男子的愚行。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57223805&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57223805%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&d=r%2F0d4hx8Jr8mhOBff1Uf6ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9f784949\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170918%26guid%3D57223805%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant&h=62add2bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170918&amp;guid=57223805&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"dc75460bee1ee56f91c87633ff07ff3d41b6ee76","tid":404324,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"活塞男好鐘意塞野<br />\n連塊鐵板都比佢塞埋"},{"pid":"a3adcf882c07400447ee6a477acf190a12fa1783","tid":404324,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18